24:12.285 --> 24:13.856
Oh, that's right.

24:13.891 --> 24:15.253
The girl.

24:15.288 --> 24:18.124
I almost forgot about the girl.

24:18.159 --> 24:20.500
No.

24:20.997 --> 24:25.131
Janice.

24:25.166 --> 24:28.772
Oh, God, please.

24:28.807 --> 24:32.204
Don't hurt me, please.

24:34.109 --> 24:35.680
