25:44.685 --> 25:47.818
- No.

25:47.853 --> 25:48.918
Yeah, you're probably right.

25:48.953 --> 25:51.789
Too much.

25:53.353 --> 25:54.924
Hey, you know what?

25:54.959 --> 25:56.662
This was fun.
I feel like we got ourselves

25:56.697 --> 25:57.993
a pretty good first draft
going here.

25:58.028 --> 26:02.096
-You agree?

26:02.131 --> 26:04.901
♪♪

26:04.936 --> 26:06.738
Yeah, I hear you.

26:06.773 --> 26:08.839
Well, Ed, it's been a blast.

26:08.874 --> 26:11.237
Great working with you.

26:11.272 --> 26:12.975
And I got to say,

26:13.010 --> 26:15.373
I'm already excited
to get going on the sequel.

26:15.408 --> 26:21.412
♪♪

26:21.447 --> 26:27.726
